{"tid":326544,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真係覺得自己好撚on9","createTime":"2017-07-18T05:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T06:12:00.000Z","uid":86629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85f02af69a5faa94cb918cf116794c5bcc436788","tid":326544,"uid":86629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"一開始就同自己講 唔好鐘意佢你<br />\n結果都係奶左野<br />\n直到你話你都鐘意我 我個下真係好開心 因為你一向都好多男仔埋身 而我只不過係一個肥矮柒毒既毒撚<br />\n你仲話放假一齊去玩 我仲plan好晒<br />\n結果放假前一個星期 你唔舒服要返香港睇醫生(我地係外國讀書)<br />\n個下我係有唔開心 唔係因為冇得同你去玩 而係驚你返左香港就唔會再理我<br />\n你返左去 就開始唔理我 其實我都知發生咩事<br />\n我問你係咪鐘意左第二個? 你仲同我講 邊有咁容易就鐘意人<br />\n我聽到你咁講仲傻到以為自己仲有希望<br />\n直到今日收到你錄音 我一聽 係你男朋友把聲<br />\n個一刻我明終於明白 我做左咁耐傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解女人可以話變就變?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a08b9c2bf9b843ec7d03c31569b1ba62e6901f6","tid":326544,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31b1635e11542fdd8756dd076618e336c092f04","tid":326544,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"講埋鐘意你都可以失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9d6c6e7d4105ee6956ae10a8bd73f6343cc22e","tid":326544,"uid":86629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac69ad028313d51aaaed0cde81aa85dc355644a4","tid":326544,"uid":90945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開始就同自己講 唔好鐘意佢你<br />\n結果都係奶左野<br />\n